DescShort: Toggle: Self +Regen, +Resist(All), +Status Protection per nearby enemy
DescLong: This power grants the user a stacking Regeneration, Resistance, and Status Protection buff for each enemy within a 10 foot radius.  The effect reaches its maximum strength at 9 enemies.  This power also grants a very large Regeneration, Resistance, and Status Protection buff regardless of nearby foes.   Equipping this Hybrid power grants a passive boost to Regeneration at all times.
